relevance_user_prompt_template:
Return JSON with keys: relevant (bool), matched_topics (list[str]), cooling_level (str: chip-level|board-level|system-level|unknown), cooling_methodology (str), rationale (str, <=40 words). Mark relevant=true for anything slightly related to thermal management/cooling/heat dissipation in electronics systems. 
Topics: {topics_json}
Cooling taxonomy: {cooling_taxonomy_json}
Title: {title}
Abstract: {abstract}

batch_relevance_user_prompt_template:
Return a JSON object with key "decisions" (list). Each decision item MUST include: id (str), relevant (bool), matched_topics (list[str]), cooling_level (one of chip-level|board-level|system-level|unknown), cooling_methodology (str), rationale (str <= 30 words). Evaluate using both title and abstract.
Topics: {topics_json}
Cooling taxonomy: {cooling_taxonomy_json}
Papers: {papers_json}
Include one decision for every input paper id.
